6 73.984-72.129 73.984 0l-11.125 254.65c-2.9609 0-5.7812 89.676 73.602-37.785 38.691-62.121 100.94-22.109 62.801 39.117l-84.16 135.09c11.793 117.27-81.285 221.63-200.24 221.63-111.13 0-201.26-90.129-201.26-201.28 0-117.13-16.371-179.8-55.09-299.45-22.52-69.621 48.203-91.402 70.398-22.777l46.844 144.77-9.2852-233c0-73.176 74-72.141 74 0l11.227 190.89 29.977-13.594 0.65234-241.1c0-73.176 73.984-72.141 73.984 0l3.2305 225.09 28.051-4.5195z\"></path>\n</svg>\n","canvasPosition":{"x":0,"y":38.000000000000114},"markdownHelp":"","settings":[],"protocolVersion":"2","canvasZoom":1},"type":"widgetGroup","groupId":"{#}MuODNOY"},"{#}cznIDKd":{"id":"{#}cznIDKd","canvas":{"position":{"x":515,"y":608}},"children":[{"childId":"{#}Q810ls4","sourcePort":"{#}cznIDKd_output_value","targetPort":"{#}Q810ls4_innerInput_inner-output-output1"}],"state":{"name":"Settings.Abort_All_Processing","reactive":true,"lastConfiguration":{"controlType":"anything","controlSettings":{"value":null},"helpText":"Linked to the 'abort' ports of all agents","group":"Settings"}},"type":"globalVariable","groupId":"{#}Q810ls4"},"{#}wgZgfrV":{"id":"{#}wgZgfrV","canvas":{"position":{"x":317,"y":227}},"children":[],"state":{"text":"# Abort Processing\n\nReacts to 'abort' events produced by the chat interface. Copy this widget for every agent you create and link it to the 'abort' input port.\n","color":"#a9b8c2","size":{"width":631,"height":200},"locked":true},"type":"note","groupId":"{#}Q810ls4"},"{#}iMDVxql":{"id":"{#}iMDVxql","canvas":{"position":{"x":-6112,"y":-7146}},"children":[],"state":{"text":"Tone Analyst v3.1\n\n* Removed set\\_status(\"TONE\\_ANALYZED\") from Phase 12 — server reads file via continueFromFile instead (fixes race condition\\\n  where Reviewer fired before TA output returned)\n* All \"Type yes/no\" prompts removed — server injects buttons after each turn\n\nReviewer v3.2\n\n* Gap interview Phase 1: \"type skip\" → server injects Skip button\n* Phase 7.5 issue backing: \"type skip\" → server injects Skip button\n* Bridge turns: server injects Continue button\n\nStyle Negotiator v1.9\n\n* Phase 3: \"Type yes/apply/no pronouns only/custom/skip\" removed — server injects 4 option buttons\n* Phase 5: now also writes sn\\_output.json alongside cv\\_assembly\\_state.json\n\nProfile Builder v1.8\n\n* Removed Phase 4 (user confirmation) and Phase 5 (process response)\n* Agent now displays built contact + profile as info bubble then writes pb\\_output.json immediately in one turn\n* Fixed agreed\\_overrides access: was treating it as array, now uses Object.values() since SN writes an object\n\nSkills Curator v1.8\n\n* Removed Phase 4 (user confirmation)\n* Displays skills list as info bubble then writes sc\\_output.json immediately\n\nHistory Formatter v1.7\n\n* Removed Phase 4 two-turn flow (AWAITING\\_CONFIRMATION intermediate state gone)\n* Displays formatted sample as info bubble then writes hf\\_output.json immediately\n* Fixed agreed\\_overrides access same as PB\n\nCredentials Formatter v1.8\n\n* Removed Phase 4 (user confirmation)\n* Displays formatted credentials then writes cf\\_output.json immediately\n\nCoverLetter Writer v1.6\n\n* Removed Phase 3 (display draft + wait) and Phase 4 (process user response)\n* Displays draft as info bubble then writes clw\\_output.json immediately\n* Fixed agreed\\_overrides access same as PB\n\n","color":"#eac43e","size":{"width":719,"height":271},"locked":false},"type":"note"},"{#}Aclj8V7":{"id":"{#}Aclj8V7","canvas":{"position":{"x":-4831,"y":-6212}},"children":[{"childId":"{#}tN0cGxD","sourcePort":"{#}Aclj8V7_innerOutput_inner-input-input1-CDDpbo","targetPort":"{#}tN0cGxD_input_input"}],"state":{"description":"","inputs":[{"name":"input1-CDDpbo","label":"tools","type":[6],"index":0,"position":{"x":1920,"y":898}}],"outputs":[],"name":"ResearchCompany","type":"custom","color":"#42a5f5","icon":"search","canvasPosition":{"x":1352.935329587277,"y":251.9173479400422},"markdownHelp":"","settings":[],"protocolVersion":"2","canvasZoom":0.6239125267098532},"type":"widgetGroup"},"{#}tN0cGxD":{"id":"{#}tN0cGxD","canvas":{"position":{"x":2170.3304331452355,"y":900.0785941463063}},"children":[{"childId":"{#}DiDuip7","sourcePort":"{#}tN0cGxD_output_arguments","targetPort":"{#}DiDuip7_input_event"}],"state":{"dynamicInputs":{},"dynamicOutputs":{},"customState":{"name":"ResearchCompany","description":"Researches company specified in PD","arguments":[{"name":"companyName","description":"Company to research","dataType":"String","typeDefinition":"","typeDefinitionMode":"typescript","required":true},{"name":"positionTitle","description":"Position to target CV for\n","dataType":"String","typeDefinition":"","typeDefinitionMode":"typescript","required":true},{"name":"sector","description":"Targeted companies sector for research\n","dataType":"String","typeDefinition":"","typeDefinitionMode":"typescript","required":true}],"timeout":10},"variantId":"tool","service":{"name":"kemu.io.ai-agent","version":"1.8.2","title":"AI Agent","description":"Define AI agents and tools for automated workflows","processor":"js","widgetUI":true,"settingsUI":false,"eventEmitter":true,"ignoreParentEvents":false,"svgIcon":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<svg width=\"1200pt\" height=\"1200pt\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 1200 1200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n <path d=\"m875.64 681.36-189.72-82.801c-45.961-19.922-82.559-56.52-102.48-102.48l-82.801-189.72c-6.4805-14.762-27.359-14.762-33.719 0l-82.801 189.72c-20.039 45.961-56.641 82.559-102.48 102.48l-190.08 82.922c-14.641 6.4805-14.762 27.238 0 33.719l193.44 85.441c45.719 20.281 82.199 57 102 103.08l80.039 186.12c6.3594 14.762 27.359 14.879 33.84 0l82.68-189.6c19.922-45.84 56.52-82.441 102.48-102.48l189.72-82.801c14.762-6.3594 14.762-27.238 0-33.719zm-210.84-6.9609c-3 6.7188-9.6016 10.801-16.559 10.801-2.3984 0-4.8008-0.48047-7.1992-1.4414-64.078-28.078-114.72-78.719-142.68-142.8-4.0781-9.1211 0.12109-19.801 9.2383-23.762 9.1211-3.9609 19.68 0.238